<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَإِفْرَاطٍ وَتَشْدِيدِ لِغَالي<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَتَصْحِيحِ النَّصِيحَةِ غَيْرَ غِشٍّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يُمَازِجُ صَفْوَهَا يَوْمًا بِحَالِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَيَحْرِصُ فِي إتِّبَاعُ النَّصُ جَهْدًا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَعَ الإِحْسَانِ فِي كُلَّ الفِعَالِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَلا يُصْغِي لِغَيْرِ النَّصِ طُرًا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَلا يَعْبَأَ بِآرَاءِ الرِّجَالِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَسِتُّ مَشَاهِدٍ لِلْقَلْبِ فِيهَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَلامَاتٌ عَنِ الدَّاءِ العُضَالِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَيَشْهَدُ مِنْهُ لِلرَّحْمَنِ يَوْمًا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِمَا أَسْدَى عَلَيْهِ مِنَ الفِضَالِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَيَشْهَدُ مِنْهُ تَقْصِيرًا وَعَجْزًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>بِحَقِّ اللهِ فِي كُلِّ الخِلالِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَقَلْبٌ لَيْسَ يَشْهَدُهَا سَقِيمٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَمَنْكُوسٌ لِفِعْلِ الخَيْرِ قَالي<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَإِنْ رُمْتَ النَّجَاةَ غَدًا وَتَرْجُوا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>نَعِيمًا لا يَصِيرُ إِلَى زَوَالِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>نَعِيمٌ لا يُبِيدُ وَلَيْسَ يَفْنَى<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بِدَارِ الخُلْدِ فِي غُرَفٍ عَوَالِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>فَلا تُشْرِكْ بِرَبِّكَ قَطُّ شَيْئًا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
